JD if you go to JDs website and look at the rankings of other ecommerce companies versus JD you will see that JD is absolutely leaving them in the dust It is absolutely critical important though for this company to continue on with the pace they have in investing back into this company That is because as big as JD is now they are still only about the size of a Target or Lowes here in the US The company that has and maintains the big number one slot in ecommerce is the company that will win Think about what happens here in this country when you think about buying online You think about Amazon You dont think about the much smaller competitors And here is the critical thing they have even managed to make eBay be a very distant second What that means is JD has the opportunity I believe to even make baba be a distant second
